  "title": "Project Engineer",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Responsibility:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Prepare shop-drawings and follow-up subsequent comments.</li><li>Attend project safety meeting and site co-ordination meeting.</li><li>Arrangement of work according to Builder's work program.</li><li>Schedule and arrange site acess arrangement for delivery.</li><li>Monitor materials delivery schedule.</li><li>Monitor daily work progress and feedback.</li><li>Implement variation work upon receiving new drawings.</li><li>Conduct follow up site testing.</li><li>Update construction drawing and follow up with draughting update.</li><li>Commissioning of project equipment.</li><li>Prepare as-built drawings, operation and maintenance manual.</li><li>Carry out duties in accordance with QEHS policy, procedures.</li><li>Performed Ad-hoc duties assigned.</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirement:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Diploma in Electrical Engineering or equivalent Diploma holder or above.</li><li>Team Player, Independent and proactive individual.</li></ul>",
